}

### Get Instructor Wallet
# Returns wallet information for a specific instructor
GET {{baseUrl}}/instructors/{{instructorId}}/wallet
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Request Withdrawal
# Requests a withdrawal from an instructor's wallet
